{
  "stem": "8703.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the sent spies to follow the people where they are going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the time when they found out in Warsaw that they are taking the people to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was the reason, if I can remember, the chairman of the Judenrat committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Adam-- I, I forgot right now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His first name was Adam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He committed suicide because he, he didn't want to be part of the liquidating in this way of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was the end of Chmielnik.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In Skarzysko-Kamienna there was already when we came, there were a lot of Jewish people already over there from various cities.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was transferred.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were three camps really, not one-- A, B, and C.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A and B was a bet-- well, camps very bad also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But C was the worst of all three of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In Werk C, Jewish life wasn't worth it a penny.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All the sadists-- it was a haven for the sadists to do whatever they, they wished, whatever they wanted just with the Jewish people-- beating, killing even.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In first place, on top were the [NON-ENGLISH,] the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The Ukrainians behaved like animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were-- they supposed to watch us around the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were closed in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They supposed to watch nobody should escape from the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But instead they were watching-- they were-- they were-- they came to the barracks, and they were looking in through the windows.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And if they saw any money-- that somebody's taking out money or they're exchanging any money, they called them out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the second day, the third or sec-- second or third fay when we were there is one man from our city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He called them out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, he was afraid, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
